{"type":"message","id":"1c9104ac","parentId":"739a6bff","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:38:09.838Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-28 22:38 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。搜索关键词：企业数字化转型 2026、智能安防行业动态、IT运维服务市场、网络系统集成趋势。请整理3-5条关键信息，每条包含：标题、摘要、启示。保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1774708689826}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbb7fc50","parentId":"1c9104ac","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:38:16.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for the latest industry trends related to 道简网络's business areas: enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"f5c1592b45b6d82f5f128fc7792f79fcf149ad74f3cd4b9c576bb1ec2b0f668a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hdk0z1y0o7gj_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":77,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42071,"totalTokens":42265,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0000924,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00504852,"total":0.00517602}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774708689832}}
{"type":"message","id":"630b21a5","parentId":"fbb7fc50","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:38:16.241Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hdk0z1y0o7gj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774708696238}}
{"type":"message","id":"e67f6bd1","parentId":"630b21a5","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:38:20.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for the latest industry trends related to 道简网络's business. Let me search for multiple keywords in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"63ed80c1fe5fa907b95a30cfb759f78a72854999a84e3e6f791e0ab261e9abdf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yd8yqfnsy6xw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新动态趋势\" 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yd8yqfnsy6xw_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yd8yqfnsy6xw_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务市场趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yd8yqfnsy6xw_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":850,"output":199,"cacheRead":41930,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42979,"cost":{"input":0.00025499999999999996,"output":0.00023879999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0012579,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017517}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774708696241}}
